Technical assistance to MOH and Districts to improve overall coordination and management of national immunisation programme focusing on equity-focused immunisation programmes : 
i) Strategic planning, programme design and development;
ii) Assessing and identifying gaps in vaccine forecasting and supply planning, and implementing strategies and tools to improve forecasting practices including data quality, methods and processes
iii) Cold chain systems strengthening;
iv) Immunization equity assessment and equity-focused programming for the marginalised and underserved population (Equity-focused programming); vi) Support with planning, implementation and monitoring of the MR SIA follow up campaign, IPV catch up campaign and TCV introduction

